data.description: Welcome Home to the Village at Concord Crossing in Johnstown! Offering 2 Master Suites! One on Main Floor and one upstairs! Plus 3rd Bedroom which is located on main floor with attached 3rd full bath!  Enjoy the Open Great Room, DIning & KItchen space with fabulous flow for entertaining! Kitchen includes granite counters, white cabinets, & updated SS appliances! The Great Room includes cozy Gas Fireplace & Cathedral Ceilings! Bonus to enjoy the 4 Seasons Room for morning coffee, a good book or perhaps the ideal office space!  Main Floor Laundry and wonderful storage space and Tons of Natural Light throughout!  Covered front porch & patio space in back!  Walking distance to Bike Path, Johnstown Schools, & Downtown Johnstown!  Home Sweet Home!
